Method Detail

bind

public Term bind(Variable var,
                 Term term)
Bind a specified variable to an other term in this substitution. If the substitution previously contained a mapping term for the variable, the old term value is replaced.

Parameters:
var - the variable to bind.
term - the term to be bound to var.
Returns:
the previous term value associated with var, or null if there was no mapping term for var.
Throws:
java.lang.NullPointerException - if var == null || term == null.
